{"manifest_version":1,"info":{"id":"zain_backup","name":"Zain's Backup","author":"iamzainnnn","version":"v35","changelog":"V35 — Changelogs\n\n🆕 Added / Enabled\n\n- Now you can send Stories to DMs by long-pressing the ⌲ icon.\n- Saved content is now accessible directly from DMs.\n- Enabled Multiple Notes support (not functional yet).\n- Brought back voice and media replies while responding to messages.\n- Enabled animated themes for eligible accounts.\n- Reintroduced voice and selfie replies on Stories.\n- You can now share voice messages from DMs to Stories.\n- Enabled more layouts for the Homecoming experience.\n- Introduced Instants Recap formats. (You can now share your Instants recaps to Stories.)\n- Enabled profile music highlights.\n- Increased the limit for pinned posts.\n- Added support for custom Story fonts for eligible accounts.\n- Enabled quick reactions while replying from the unified composer experience.\n\n🔄 Updated / Improved\n\n- Updated the Stories viewer list.\n- Redesigned several UI elements across the app.\n- Updated the Instagram logo.\n- Improved Stories viewer animations and transitions.\n- Enhanced Stories blur effects and visual polish.\n- Improved Reels audio playback stability.\n- Refined Homecoming layout behavior and navigation.\n- Improved feed and sharing interactions across multiple surfaces.\n- Improved Stories creation and sharing experience with additional editing tools and enhancements.\n- Improved Direct connectivity and message delivery reliability.\n- Refined Reels viewer controls and playback interactions.\n- Enhanced profile customization options for eligible accounts.\n- Improved notification accuracy and badge synchronization.\n- New animation while swiping through Instants.\n\n🪄 Restored\n\n- Restored the ability to reply to liked and reshared-by-friends bubbles.\n\n🛠 Fixed\n\n- Fixed glitches while opening the Stories viewer.\n- Fixed video zoom issues in the feed viewer.\n- Fixed several bottom sheet and viewer-related issues.\n- Applied multiple reliability, memory leak, and stability fixes across Reels, Stories, DMs, and media components.\n\n🚫 Removed\n\n- Removed unnecessary midcards from Stories."},"backup":{"89057:":["0: : true"],"53982:":["0: : true"],"122807:":["0: : true","1: : true"],"96703:":["0: : true"],"69718:":["4: : true"],"120159:":["0: : true"],"55842:":["0: : true"],"70831:":["11: : false","15: : true","13: : true","10: : true","12: : true"],"73763:":["30: : true","29: : true","27: : true","26: : true","18: : true","17: : false","12: : true","6: : true","5: : true","3: : true","2: : true","1: : true","0: : true","21: : true","15: : true","4: : true","16: : true","13: : true","14: : true","8: : true","7: : 10"],"101332:":["14: : true","9: : false","6: : true","2: : true","0: : true","4: : true","10: : true"],"50769:":["23: : false"],"64040:":["1: : false","0: : false","2: : false","3: : false"],"124097:":["1: : true","0: : true"],"60946:":["0: : false"],"83747:":["0: : true"],"102713:":["0: : true"],"77485:":["4: : true"],"106908:":["0: : true"],"102290:":["2: : true","1: : true","0: : true"],"101311:":["0: : true","1: : true"],"121677:":["2: : true","0: : true"],"106882:":["0: : false"],"103620:":["1: : true","0: : true"],"105615:":["9: : true","7: : true","5: : true","3: : false","2: : true","1: : true","8: : true","6: : false","4: : true"],"103969:":["0: : true"],"101226:":["3: : true"],"108768:":["0: : true","2: : true"],"109190:":["0: : true"],"121581:":["3: : true","2: : true","1: : true","0: : true"],"123680:":["0: : true","1: : true"],"51328:":["9: : -100"],"98941:":["1: : 1"],"116187:":["0: : 1"],"57372:":["0: : true"],"86043:":["0: : true","1: : true"],"92436:":["0: : true"],"49223:":["149: : true"],"25054:":["5: : true","4: : true","3: : true","2: : true","1: : true"],"27497:":["5: : true"],"27868:":["3: : true"],"29309:":["5: : false"],"30645:":["0: : true"],"36085:":["0: : true"],"37516:":["0: : true"],"38658:":["26: : true","24: : true","23: : tru